author: Greg Morabito
title: The Rock Has an Epiphany at In-N-Out Burger
text: share Yesterday, Dwayne “ t he Rock” Johnson took a break from his usual routine of eating cod and pumping iron and decided to hit up a location of fast-food favorite In-N-Out Burger . The wrestler-turned-movie star was so blown away by his * first ever In-N-Out experience * that he decided to write an ode to the restaurant and its staff on Instagram. It’s not clear whether Johnson actually ate anything, or if he was just getting food for his wife and daughter. But the Rock promised to return in his tux on Sunday night if his movie Maona wins an Academy Award, so he can pig out: A post shared by therock (@therock) on Feb 23, 2017 at 6:42pm PST
